  "comment": "Sunrise 2 is the first blinder with LED source which equals the brightness of conventional projectors based around DWE 2x650W halogen lamps. It's equipped with 2x100W COB LED 3.200 K and an optical glass that is able to reproduce the projection angle, colour temperature, dimmer ramp and brightness of a fluorescent bulb. The electronic Sunrise 2 also offers many other key points such as the option to control each LED independently in pixel2pixel and can be taken advantage of a dedicated channel to the strobe, in addition to the selection of different dimmer curves.",
